text: Charlie Chan in Egypt is a 1935 American mystery movie directed by Louis King and is the 11th movie in the Charlie Chan series. It stars Warner Oland, Pat Paterson, Thomas Beck, Rita Hayworth, Jameson Thomas, Frank Conroy and was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * * * Category:1935 movies Category:1930s mystery movies Category:American mystery movies Category:Movies directed by Louis King Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies set in Egypt Category:Charlie Chan
